    <item>
      <title>Ncube表示，尽管遭受损失，津巴布韦仍将保留本币并调整计划</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-23/-zwl-usd-zimbabwe-to-keep-local-dollar-despite-losses-revamp-plans-ncube-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[津巴布韦财政部长姆苏利·恩库贝 (Mthuli Ncube) 表示，津巴布韦计划保留本国货币，尽管财政和货币当局正在制定新的货币改革计划，但这种货币在一年中的每个交易日都在贬值。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-23/-zwl-usd-zimbabwe-to-keep-local-dollar-despite-losses-revamp-plans-ncube-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 23 Mar 2024 18:38:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
