      <title>拜登签署 1.2 万亿美元拨款法案，结束停工威胁</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-23/biden-signs-1-2-trillion-funding-bill-to-end-shutdown-threat</link>
      <description><![CDATA[总统乔·拜登签署了一项 1.2 万亿美元的融资计划，使美国政府能够维持到 9 月 30 日，避免部分关闭。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-23/biden-signs-1-2-trillion-funding-bill-to-end-shutdown-threat</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 23 Mar 2024 17:13:37 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>加纳前两个月可可作物贸易顺差较低</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-23/ghana-s-low-cocoa-crop-hammers-trade-surplus-in-first-two-months</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加纳可可收成减少，对该国的对外支付状况造成影响，前两个月贸易顺差下降了一半以上，对塞地货币构成风险。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-23/ghana-s-low-cocoa-crop-hammers-trade-surplus-in-first-two-months</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 23 Mar 2024 16:56:43 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
