      <title>被禁止的交易员在监管机构抓获之前继续工作多年</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-23/banned-trader-kept-working-for-years-before-regulator-caught-him</link>
      <description><![CDATA[马克·瓦伦丁 (Mark Valentine) 是一位前金融业高管，近 20 年前，他因激进的交易行为而被加拿大监管机构禁止，但他从未真正退出。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-23/banned-trader-kept-working-for-years-before-regulator-caught-him</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 23 Mar 2024 16:09:53 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
